   Xie, Jiangjian, Beijing Forestry Univ, State Key Lab Efficient Prod Forest Resources, Beijing 100083, Peoples R China.
   Lin, Congtian, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Zool, Sci Data Ctr, Beijing 100101, Peoples R China.
   Lin, Congtian, Natl Basic Sci Data Ctr, Beijing 100190, Peoples R China.
   Chang, Jiang, Chinese Res Inst Environm Sci, State Key Lab Environm Criteria \& Risk Assessment, Beijing 100085, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.avrs.2026.100361},
