   Yang, Zifeng, Guangzhou Med Univ, Guangzhou Inst Resp Hlth,Affiliated Hosp 1, Natl Clin Res Ctr Resp Dis, State Key Lab Resp Dis, Guangzhou, Peoples R China.},
