   Tenekecioglu, Erhan, Hlth Sci Univ, Bursa Educ \& Res Hosp, Dept Cardiol, Bursa, Turkiye.
   Tenekecioglu, Erhan, Erasmus Univ, Dept Cardiol, Thoraxctr, Erasmus MC, Rotterdam, Netherlands.
