   Hoos, Holger H., RWTH Aaachen Univ, Chair AI Methodol, D-52056 Aachen, Germany.
   Hoos, Holger H., Univ British Columbia, Dept Comp Sci, Vancouver, BC V6T 1Z4, Canada.},
