   Wu, Mou; Zhong, Liangji; Jin, Guonian, Hubei Univ Sci \& Technol, Sch Comp Sci \& Technol, Xianning 437100, Peoples R China.
   Wu, Mou, Hubei Univ Sci \& Technol, Lab Optoelect Informat \& Intelligent Control, Xianning 437100, Peoples R China.
   Xiong, Neal, Sul Ross State Univ, Dept Comp Sci \& Math, Alpine, TX 79830 USA.},
DOI = {10.3390/app122312432},
Article-Number = {12432},
Keywords = {facial attribute recognition; feature extraction; deep learning; random
   forest},
Keywords-Plus = {RANDOM FOREST},
